results.name: Inverse permutation to A308021 (Recamán variant).
comment: More precisely, A308021 is by definition injective but presently only conjectured to be a permutation. Until that property is proved, we define this sequence as a(n) = index of the n-th smallest term of A308021.
results.author: _M. F. Hasler_, May 10 2019
